description: Element Container for Put COD Award Information Override Data.

validation.validation: You can't override these fields for student awards that aren't loans: Academic Year Dates, Loan Period Dates, or Loan Fee Percent.
Specify a Loan Fee Percent that matches a Loan Fee Line Loan Fee Percent for the Student Award Grouper.
To update the COD status to "Ready to Transmit", specify at least 1 award with the same sequence number, and an award item that has an accepted amount or that originated to COD.
You can't override the HPPA Indicator for student awards that aren't Federal Direct Unsubsidized Loans.
